{"tid":752884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於連登對女性的立場(2)","createTime":"2018-07-23T07:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T14:57:57.000Z","uid":59328,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2a21a29bba738e2c1902a32e5ddc67a083473b11","tid":752884,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"之前有新聞揭發一些商店的走黑點，女士們受訪時表示害怕不安。結果引來連登仔評擊，認為女士著裙就預左會走光，仲話女士天性就係暴露身體吸引異性有咩所謂、扮曬野。但當之前有癡漢港鐵偷拍裙底照時，竟然一眾連登仔又一面倒恥笑佢。係咪因為癡漢係耶撚所以改變立場？"},{"pid":"c9dee14e6e1761d47506d97fd071d6eec9158335","tid":752884,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2424b88d6596663ef13d5cbadfc17fa0ca15a89d","tid":752884,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57bda360f29ab797c2d662dc5d34d0353b19f337","tid":752884,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T06:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a558f20e64b9595e40f66cf817e375293d0c13f1","tid":752884,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T07:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c3d038d08660085117c371ae96755ffd337bde","tid":752884,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b4e5534108aa7566079a6a55c04e044955522d","tid":752884,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}